    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the gratin is cooking, wrap your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> in your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong>, then transfer to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the bacon is slightly crispy – this is your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>wrapped in bacon</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
